{"tid":1768744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急，Joshua Wong 香港眾志入一入黎","createTime":"2019-12-04T09:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T13:16:52.000Z","uid":267881,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"be54bd5073275ac4bcbdd83080e5d295236fdf86","tid":1768744,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:49:22.000Z","msg":"你打緊國際戰線，知唔知自己有幾重要，國際上愈黎愈多人認識你地，靠你地認識香港情況<br />\n<br />\n但係呢，你地Facebook冇英文版<br />\n你地個網站有英文版但唔update<br />\n完全冇提意大利戰況<br />\n<br />\n你地成功推動意粉國會表態撐港，好叻<br />\n之前有提過總理、外交部長、參眾議長撐港<br />\n但google根本冇英文Source<br />\n你地冇提供Source又冇提供英文版<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以做多少少<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英文版！英文版！英文版！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我有試過打你個3字頭電話，唔撚通呀"},{"pid":"fcaa00583f2027459387fb0832e06c02a5cbd5de","tid":1768744,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"d491ba87ef9f707723c2537772ba7408d387552a","tid":1768744,"uid":6980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"推俾gphone睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c965aed4e16a7c97d83bf11c71deb4099aa313","tid":1768744,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"Twitter 有英文"},{"pid":"8ccf1419976119398b0af2cbe274e43910b9b3f2","tid":1768744,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T09:52:33.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b92bfb1c25ade333a62d492ed1822ff06d177674","tid":1768744,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"(感謝list on Twitter!) 通過Uyghur